10 Feb 2012 20:04






I was thinking about this SCP today and I've had an idea (I know this is an old article, but if you want a story, this could be included in an exploration log of sorts. Perhaps one where someone fell asleep or ran into a pipe and was knocked unconscious?).

On to the idea:

What is the circulatory system?

Various tubes, or if you want, pipes!

Imagine seeing a few pipes linked to a suspended heart's pulmonary arteries, and more pipes branching from the vena cava - the heart still beating as material is pumped through.

Imagine a corpse with a pipe running through its chest. The body could be still (barely) alive - connected to the plumbing. Maybe this is the reason for the screaming. The intense pain of molten iron, or insects, or whatever it is pumping through your bloodstream?

My idea really creeps me out, and the thought of being sustained with a pipe running through your body makes me queasy. What do you think?





